openapi: 3.0.3

paths:

      parameters:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Response code is 200
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object

                  data:
                    type: array
                    items:
                      type: object

                        id:

                        name:
                          type: string
                        retired:
                          type: boolean
                  total_pages:
                    type: integer
                  current_page:
                    type: integer
                  per_page:
                    type: integer
              example:
                data:
                  - id: 4
                    name: sanfrecce-osaka
                    retired: false
                total_pages: 1
                current_page: 1
                per_page: 25

          description: Response code is 204

              schema:
                type: string
  "/v1/users/{id}":
    get:
      summary: 'api/v1/users #show'
      parameters:
        - name: id
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Response code is 200
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  id:
                    type: integer
                  name:
                    type: string
                  retired:
                    type: boolean
              example:
                id: 3
                name: smith1045
                retired: false

            application/json:
